message.body: If my mucus is green yellow do I have to get antibiotics?

Eeeeeewww. If you have a fever you would need antibiotics ...drink lots of water. Did you say you got the box in the mail? Did you get my mom's check as well? And did she send one check or two? She's missing one. And any birthday ideas? Love you
No fever yet. I did get the box, thank you! Got Nain's check, just one and money I think for my birthday. I'll think about it.
OK i love you and miss you
Love you and miss you too
